    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BEFORE YOU BUY!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are launching Collinwood in Early Access to offer you a way to support ongoing development and get involved in the creative process. We’re offering the game at a small price for early supporters, with the chance to directly influence its future through your feedback. While the game is still in its early stages and may feel like a demo, your support helps us expand and improve Collinwood. Let’s make it better together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249910/extras/c7a7a4c78b38c9bf75cfa594746ee62b.poster.avif?t=1749125878\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249910/extras/c7a7a4c78b38c9bf75cfa594746ee62b.webm?t=1749125878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249910/extras/c7a7a4c78b38c9bf75cfa594746ee62b.mp4?t=1749125878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a vibrant and peaceful sandbox teeming with wildlife and nature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BUILD YOUR BASE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your base expands as you progress, unlocking new game mechanics like cooking, farming, crafting, and hunting practice fields.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249910/extras/a2df01944936e686c147911400857e1b.poster.avif?t=1749125878\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249910/extras/a2df01944936e686c147911400857e1b.webm?t=1749125878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249910/extras/a2df01944936e686c147911400857e1b.mp4?t=1749125878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SURVIVE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dangerous animals inhabit parts of Collinwood, so it's best to keep your distance. (<i>For a more peaceful experience, ZEN mode offers exploration, camping, relaxation, music, and more, without any threats.)</i></p>",
